        <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Module Contract\/ \:</para>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  Read and parse DOCX documents, extracting lines with metadata, tables, and attachments into UnstructuredDocument. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>\par \b Scope\/ \:  Feature and metadata extraction from documents. \par \b Input\/ \:  [File path (str), parameters (Optional[dict]) — document on disk.] \par \b Output\/ \:  [UnstructuredDocument with lines, tables, attachments, and warnings.] \par \b Links\/ \:  [USES_API(9): <ref refid="namespacededoc_1_1data__structures" kindref="compound">dedoc.data_structures</ref>.*; USES_API(8): dedoc.readers.BaseReader] \par \b Invariants\/ \:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>read() ALWAYS returns an UnstructuredDocument. \par \b Rationale\/ \:</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
